the 2026 Winter Olympics in Milan, Italy.\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.6006881564906907, \"rank\": 0.6630616246058291, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}, {\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bill Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.C._Milan\", \"score\": 0.9999999980964276, \"rank\": 1.9038843727632676e-09, \"text\": \"Milan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.C._Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.C._Milan\"}, {\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999946950187875, \"rank\": 5.30492712589774e-06, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  \\\"I think it's important for guys to go,\\\" Guerin, the United States' general manager for both the 4 Nations Face-Off and theOlympics, said during a sitdown withThe Athleticat last week'sNHLGMs meetings in South Florida.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.709742713766769e-38, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hey look, there is some guys that are going to be a lock for both teams.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there are going to be guys that are on the bubble.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If they have not played in the playoffs or meaningful games in a long time - or,ever- I want to see how they perform.\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, in that respect, I think the world championships are extremely important.\\\"\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not difficult to determine what bubble players Guerin has in mind.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The list may include defensemen likeZach WerenskiandSeth Jonesand forwards likeClayton Keller,Troy Terry,Trevor Zegras,Tage Thompson,Alex Tuchand even Guerin's ownMinnesota Wildplayer,Matt Boldy.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boldy has been a key contributor on gold medal-winning United States teams, like the 2021 World Junior Championship team, but Guerin has been publicly critical of his first two postseasons with the Wild.\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1538, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.709742713766769e-38, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So using him as an example, if he wants to be tapped for either of the upcoming best-on-best tournaments and the Wild miss the playoffs, he may want to strongly consider putting off his summer golf by a month.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Guerin says this is not so much an edict as a suggestion.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to see commitment, and if a trip to the Caribbean is more important than the world championships, then you are not really committed,\\\" Guerin said.\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our player pool is pretty substantial now.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not going to say, black and white, 'If you do this, then yes.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do this, then no.'\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we are trying to put the best team on the ice that we possibly can.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we also want guys that are committed.\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I get there are situations, like guys are getting married, guys are having babies, guys are injured.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I get that.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But if you are not?\\\"\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  If you are not, seeya in Ostrava and Prague, Czechia, from May 10 to 16 as the United States strives to win its second World Championship ever and first since1933.\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2540, \"end\": 2547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ostrava\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.459889423388049e-20, \"text\": \"Ostrava\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http: