p://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are not tied together that if you do not go you are off a list - there is nothing like that - but the reality is if someone's going to go there and someone's going to play well, someone's going to get somebody's attention.\\\"\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  Nash, the formerColumbus Blue Jacketscaptain, said two years ago when he was assistant GM for Canada's World Championship team, \\\"It almost became that you were begging players to go, and I already feel like this time is different.\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4436, \"end\": 4438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8677166535458415e-33, \"text\": \"GM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\"}, {\"begin\": 4443, \"end\": 4449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999937597316676, \"rank\": 6.240307659951942e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From talking with Doug Armstrong and (Hockey Canada vice president of hockey operations) Scott Salmond, this is the start of the process over the next few years, with this, the 4 Nations Face-off and the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4598, \"end\": 4612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doug_Armstrong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9857680119495513e-53, \"text\": \"Doug Armstrong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doug_Armstrong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doug_Armstrong\"}, {\"begin\": 4618, \"end\": 4631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hockey Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hockey_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 4669, \"end\": 4674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Steiner\", \"score\": 0.9993648400985893, \"rank\": 0.0006355631422108466, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Steiner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Steiner\"}, {\"begin\": 4675, \"end\": 4682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Salmond\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.424231432802604e-14, \"text\": \"Salmond\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Salmond\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Salmond\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The international game is a little different.\", \"from\": 4795, \"to\": 4841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not exactly like the NHL.\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4868, \"end\": 4871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1885035568358134e-43, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Different systems, different styles of play.\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's important for guys to come get the experience in the worlds and have success to get the best opportunity to make the next step, whether it's 4 Nations or the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 4918, \"to\": 5091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, Nash and Armstrong are offering a hint a little softer than Guerin's blunter one - but if someone likeMontreal CanadienscaptainNick Suzukiwants to play in the 4 Nations Face-off or the 2026 Olympics, he should still probably be in Prague this May.\", \"from\": 5093, \"to\": 5356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5109, \"end\": 5113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graham_Nash\", \"score\": 0.9999983238699719, \"rank\": 1.6467517428213006e-06, \"text\": \"Nash\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graham_Nash\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graham_Nash\"}, {\"begin\": 5118, \"end\": 5127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"score\": 0.9999999962492438, \"rank\": 3.75079412447239e-09, \"text\": \"Armstrong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lance_Armstrong\"}, {\"begin\": 5169, \"end\": 5175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 5340, \"end\": 5346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"score\": 0.999046681811165, \"rank\": 0.0009542278716506399, \"text\": \"Prague\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This especially makes sense when you consider how torturous it will be to select a roster ahead of next year's Feb. 12 to 20 4 Nations Face-Off, which will feature the U.S., Canada, Sweden and Finland.\", \"from\": 5358, \"to\": 5559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5532, \"end\": 5538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999937597316676, \"rank\": 6.240307659951942e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5540, \"end\": 5546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 5.795430620438321e-13, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5551, \"end\": 5558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.958543105900866e-19, \"text\": \"Finland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will feature 23-player rosters, with three of those players being goaltenders.\", \"from\": 5560, \"to\": 5648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That means each team can only have 20 skaters - or one extra forward and one extra defenseman.\", \"from\": 5649, \"to\": 5743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once the tournament starts, if you sustain multiple injuries, there is no reserve list or taxi squad to choose from.\", \"from\": 5744, \"to\": 5860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So Guerin especially wants bubble players who miss this year's Stanley Cup playoffs to attend the World Championship so the management team, which is led by GM Brett Peterson (Florida Panthersassistant GM), can ascertain which players could fill roles they are otherwise not accustomed to.\", \"from\": 5862, \"to\": 6151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5865, \"end\": 5871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 6019, \"end\": 6021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8677166535458415e-33, \"text\": \"GM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\"}, {\"begin\": 6038, \"end\": 6045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"score\": 0.999797933142065, \"rank\": 0.00014495497364126116, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\"}, {\"begin\": 6064, \"end\": 6066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8677166535458415e-33, \"text\": \"GM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most players in the upcoming tournaments play top-six and top power-play roles on their NHL teams.\", \"from\": 6153, \"to\": 6251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6241, \"end\": 6244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1885035568358134e-43, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that may not be the case on talent-rich rosters in the 4 Nations Face-Off and Olympics.The Athleticprojected what the U.S. roster could look likeunder Guerin last month, for a sense of its depth.\", \"from\": 6252, \"to\": 6451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6407, \"end\": 6413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guerin plans to be at the World Championship to begin the evaluation process for the upcoming tournaments.\", \"from\": 6455, \"to\": 6561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  \\\"These are short tournaments,\\\" Guerin said.\", \"from\": 6563, \"to\": 6621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6609, \"end\": 6615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Almost everybody that'll be on the teams is a power-play guy or a penalty-kill guy or a first-line center, winger, top-pair defenseman.\", \"from\": 6622, \"to\": 6758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Almost everybody on the teams are star players.\", \"from\": 6759, \"to\": 6806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we want to see, 'Can you buy in?\", \"from\": 6807, \"to\": 6842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can you be happy with less ice time than you normally get?\", \"from\": 6843, \"to\": 6901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Will you be supportive of the guys that are on the power play if you are not?'\", \"from\": 6902, \"to\": 6980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need good guys that are going to be good teammates and guys that will fall in and be willing to accept roles that may be uncomfortable.\", \"from\": 6982, \"to\": 7121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To me, that's so important.\", \"from\": 7122, \"to\": 7149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's an important reason for guys to do these world championships year in and year out - not just this year when it's a 4 Nations year or an Olympic year - so we know who you are.\", \"from\": 7150, \"to\": 7331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not just the hockey part.\", \"from\": 7333, \"to\": 7364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's that we get to know you a little bit because, to me, the buy-in factor is so enormous.\", \"from\": 7365, \"to\": 7456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not just skating, shooting and passing.\", \"from\": 7457, \"to\": 7501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the heart.\", \"from\": 7502, \"to\": 7517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the emotion.\", \"from\": 7518, \"to\": 7535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's what you are willing to do for the team.\\\"\", \"from\": 7536, \"to\": 7582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first six players for each country in the 4 Nations Face-Off must be announced by the end of June.\", \"from\": 7584, \"to\": 7686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There will not be any practices until Feb. 10-11 before the tournament starts in one American city and one Canadian city Feb. 12.\", \"from\": 7687, \"to\": 7816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7772, \"end\": 7780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.6006881564906907, \"rank\": 0.6630616246058291, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}, {\"begin\": 7794, \"end\": 7802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999999998408384, \"rank\": 1.5918590617107423e-10, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guerin has conducted a few meetings already and has checked a few boxes, like selecting his staff, for one.\", \"from\": 7818, \"to\": 7925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7818, \"end\": 7824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something USA Hockey is expected to announce next month.\", \"from\": 7927, \"to\": 7990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7944, \"end\": 7954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA Hockey\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guerin would not reveal which shoulders he has tapped, but there is a great chance thePittsburgh Penguins'Mike Sullivan will be the head honcho behind the bench.\", \"from\": 7992, \"to\": 8153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7992, \"end\": 7998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 8103, \"end\": 8111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.991769772941815, \"rank\": 0.008298525809798158, \"text\": \"Sullivan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sullivan and Guerin have a long history together from Guerin's Penguins days, and Sullivan was supposed to coach the United States at the 2022 Olympics until the pandemic caused the NHL to pull out.\", \"from\": 8154, \"to\": 8352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8154, \"end\": 8162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.991769772941815, \"rank\": 0.008298525809798158, \"text\": \"Sullivan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\"}, {\"begin\": 8167, \"end\": 8173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 8208, \"end\": 8214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 8236, \"end\": 8244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.991769772941815, \"rank\": 0.008298525809798158, \"text\": \"Sullivan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danny_Sullivan\"}, {\"begin\": 8271, \"end\": 8284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.709742713766769e-38, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 8336, \"end\": 8339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1885035568358134e-43, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, we were well down the road with the Olympic team at the time when the rug got pulled out from under us there, so to speak,\\\" Sullivan toldThe Athleticlast month.\", \"from\": 8354, \"to\": 8526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So we had gone through a process as a group there.\", \"from\": 8527, \"to\": 8578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think that there is any better guy that's suited to lead that group with all of the experience that he's had and international play in the NHL and his experience as a manager than Billy.\\\"\", \"from\": 8579, \"to\": 8775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8727, \"end\": 8730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1885035568358134e-43, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  As for Guerin's management staff,New York RangersGM Chris Drury was supposed to be his assistant GM for the Olympics two years ago.\", \"from\": 8777, \"to\": 8923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8799, \"end\": 8805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 8825, \"end\": 8833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9583953776659204, \"rank\": 0.043410708204867685, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 8844, \"end\": 8855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Drury\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.888759037602186e-64, \"text\": \"Chris Drury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Drury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Drury\"}, {\"begin\": 8889, \"end\": 8891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8677166535458415e-33, \"text\": \"GM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guerin may have been being cagey, but he said that does not necessarily mean his managerial staff will have the same roles this time around.\", \"from\": 8924, \"to\": 9064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has a large group of American execs he can choose from: Drury,New Jersey DevilsGM Tom Fitzgerald, Panthers GM Bill Zito,San Jose SharksGM Mike Grier,Colorado AvalancheGM Chris MacFarland,Buffalo SabresGM Kevyn Adams,Calgary FlamesGM Craig Conroy and, of course, USA Hockey lifersNew York IslandersGM Lou Lamoriello andCarolina HurricanesGM Don Waddell.\", \"from\": 9066, \"to\": 9421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9090, \"end\": 9098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.6006881564906907, \"rank\": 0.6630616246058291, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}, {\"begin\": 9125, \"end\": 9130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drury_University\", \"score\": 0.99997