\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When we do this stuff, I want the focus to be on this,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 9680, \"to\": 9745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard to ask guys if they are in the middle of a playoff push to do a USA Hockey call.\\\"\", \"from\": 9746, \"to\": 9838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9821, \"end\": 9831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA Hockey\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guerin intends to have the same staff for the 2026 Olympics as he has for the 4 Nations Face-Off, for continuity's sake.\", \"from\": 9840, \"to\": 9960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not explain how excited I am,\\\" Guerin said.\", \"from\": 9962, \"to\": 10012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10000, \"end\": 10006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.241671965211986e-52, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are in it to win it.\\\"\", \"from\": 10013, \"to\": 10038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that process starts in Czechia with the World Championship.\", \"from\": 10040, \"to\": 10103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10067, \"end\": 10074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.3570408139482144e-27, \"text\": \"Czechia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\",